ADF: 0.1

🎯 TASK: Agent context — Claude execution, MCP connections, tools, memory. Two implementations: edge (Anthropic API + fetch) and local (Claude Agent SDK).

⚠ CONSTRAINTS [load-bearing]:
  - Memory writes use structured record_memory_entry tool, never raw file writes
  - MCP auth via Authorization Bearer header, never token-in-URL
  - System prompt includes memory context on every execution
  - sendMessage() / executeClaudeChat() is called only by the kernel dispatcher — never by channels directly
  - Edge MCP uses Service Binding fetch (avoids Cloudflare Worker-to-Worker 1042 error)
  - Anthropic tool_result format: { type: 'tool_result', tool_use_id, content } — NOT { id, text }

📁 FILES [advisory]:
  Edge (web/src/) — primary:
    - claude.ts: executeClaudeChat() — Anthropic Messages API with tool loop (max 10 rounds)
      - System prompt: built by operator/prompt-builder.ts from config + persona template + memory context from D1
      - Tools: conditionally assembled from operatorConfig.integrations (BizOps, GitHub, Brave, goals)
      - Cost estimation: (input*3 + output*15) / 1M
    - mcp-client.ts: McpClient class — Streamable HTTP transport
      - Constructor: { url, token, fetcher? } — fetcher is the Service Binding
      - Session management: initialize() → Mcp-Session-Id header → all subsequent calls
      - SSE response parsing for text/event-stream Content-Type
      - toAnthropicTools(): converts MCP tool definitions to Anthropic API format
      - toMcpToolName(): strips 'mcp__bizops__' prefix for MCP dispatch
    - groq.ts: askGroq() — fetch-based, no SDK dependency
    - github.ts: GitHub REST API client — fetch-based, no SDK
        - Read: getRepoTree, getFileContent, getRecentCommits, listIssues, listPullRequests, listOrgRepos
        - Write: createIssue, createBranch, getFileSha, updateFile, createPullRequest, mergePullRequest
        - CI: listWorkflowRuns (Actions API), getCombinedStatus (Status API)
        - Git Data API: createBlob, getBaseTreeSha, createTree, createGitCommit, updateRef (multi-file commits)
        - ghFetch: GitHubApiError class, retry on 500/502/503 (2x exponential backoff), rate limit detection (403/429)
        - Auth: Bearer GITHUB_TOKEN secret

  Local (src/agent/) — optional:
    - session.ts: sendMessage(channel, threadId, text) → TurnResult via Claude SDK query()
    - system-prompt.ts: buildSystemPrompt() — Kurt persona + memory entries + channel context
    - hooks.ts: makePreToolUseHook(channel), makeStopHook()
    - tools.ts: In-process SDK MCP server (aegis_memory) with record_memory_entry tool
    - code-executor.ts: Spawns Claude Code CLI in target repo, resolves repo from semantic memory

