      register_project, list_projects, get_project, update_project
    - Edge: Service Binding (env.BIZOPS.fetch), MCP Streamable HTTP, Bearer auth
    - Local: HTTP transport to https://businessops-copilot.kurt-5be.workers.dev/mcp, Bearer auth

  aegis_memory (local only):
